### 核心模块详细设计

#### 1. Skia 渲染层（直接封装，无抽象）

> **MVP 简化策略**：不设计抽象层，直接封装 Skia API。等未来需要切换后端时再抽象。

##### 1.1 SkiaCanvas 封装
```moonbit
// 直接封装，不使用 trait
type SkiaCanvas {
  priv raw: RawSkiaCanvas
  width: Int
  height: Int
}

// 基本绘制方法
fn SkiaCanvas::create(width: Int, height: Int) -> Result[SkiaCanvas, String]
fn SkiaCanvas::destroy(self: SkiaCanvas) -> Unit
fn SkiaCanvas::clear(self: SkiaCanvas, color: Color) -> Unit
fn SkiaCanvas::draw_rect(self: SkiaCanvas, rect: Rect, paint: Paint) -> Unit
fn SkiaCanvas::draw_ellipse(self: SkiaCanvas, cx: Double, cy: Double, rx: Double, ry: Double, paint: Paint) -> Unit
fn SkiaCanvas::draw_line(self: SkiaCanvas, x1: Double, y1: Double, x2: Double, y2: Double, paint: Paint) -> Unit
fn SkiaCanvas::draw_path(self: SkiaCanvas, path: SkiaPath, paint: Paint) -> Unit
fn SkiaCanvas::save_to_png(self: SkiaCanvas, filepath: String) -> Result[Unit, String]
```

##### 1.2 SkiaPath 封装
```moonbit
type SkiaPath {
  priv raw: RawSkiaPath
}

fn SkiaPath::create() -> SkiaPath
fn SkiaPath::destroy(self: SkiaPath) -> Unit
fn SkiaPath::move_to(self: SkiaPath, x: Double, y: Double) -> Unit
fn SkiaPath::line_to(self: SkiaPath, x: Double, y: Double) -> Unit
fn SkiaPath::quad_to(self: SkiaPath, cx: Double, cy: Double, x: Double, y: Double) -> Unit
fn SkiaPath::close(self: SkiaPath) -> Unit
```

